Package: sigterm
Title: Detect When R Receives 'SIGTERM'
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
  person("Aaron", "Jacobs", role = c("aut", "cre"),
         email = "atheriel@gmail.com")
  )
Maintainer: Aaron Jacobs <atheriel@gmail.com>
Description: Captures 'SIGTERM' signal sent to R and exposes a way to check if
  one has been received. This allows users to implement graceful shutdown
  functionality that might not otherwise be possible to trigger reliably.
License: Apache License (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
OS_type: unix
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
SystemRequirements: POSIX.1-2001
